ocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2528591\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 07, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ikq1665702989159.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ikq1665702989159.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ikq1665702989159.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ikq1665702989159\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Differences Between P_MSWINX and P_X11 Output\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">For enhanced printing, Uniface provides the P_MSWINX device translation table for Windows and the P_X11 table for PostScript. However, there are differences in print output produced, especially in the way colors and images are handled.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ikq1665702989159__section_w2269ab1b5b1_w2270ab1b5_w2271ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"ikq1665702989159__table_d5696e1_d5697e1_d5698e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\"></span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ikq1665702989159__table_d5696e1_d5697e1_d5698e1__entry__1\">\n Functionality\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ikq1665702989159__table_d5696e1_d5697e1_d5698e1__entry__2\">\n P_MSWINX\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ikq1665702989159__table_d5696e1_d5697e1_d5698e1__entry__3\">\n P_X11\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ikq1665702989159__table_d5696e1_d5697e1_d5698e1__entry__1\">Color printing <div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"ikq1665702989159__note_w2392ab1b5b1b1b3b9b1b1b1_w2393ab1b5b1b1b3b9b1b1_w2394ab1b5b1b1b3b9b1_w2395ab1b5b1b1b3b9_w2396ab1b5b1b1b3_w2397ab1b5b1b1_w2398ab1b5b1_w2399ab1b5_w2400ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> Color printing\n                           is only possible if <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Print using colors</span> is selected\n                           in the Print Job Model.</div>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ikq1665702989159__table_d5696e1_d5697e1_d5698e1__entry__2\">\n Only index colors can be printed.\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ikq1665702989159__table_d5696e1_d5697e1_d5698e1__entry__3\">\n Index colors can be printed.\n <p class=\"p\">Web colors (which are set using the Background and Foreground widget properties) can be printed.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"ikq1665702989159__note_w2401ab1b5b1b1b3b9b1b5b3_w2402ab1b5b1b1b3b9b1b5_w2403ab1b5b1b1b3b9b1_w2404ab1b5b1b1b3b9_w2405ab1b5b1b1b3_w2406ab1b5b1b1_w2407ab1b5b1_w2408ab1b5_w2409ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> It is not possible to combine index colors and web colors in a single component.</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ikq1665702989159__table_d5696e1_d5697e1_d5698e1__entry__1\">\n Color code 0 in labels\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ikq1665702989159__table_d5696e1_d5697e1_d5698e1__entry__2\">\n Transparent background\n <div class=\"p\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"ikq1665702989159__fig_w2272ab1b5b1b1b3b9b3b3b1b1_w2273ab1b5b1b1b3b9b3b3b1_w2274ab1b5b1b1b3b9b3b3_w2275ab1b5b1b1b3b9b3_w2276ab1b5b1b1b3b9_w2277ab1b5b1b1b3_w2278ab1b5b1b1_w2279ab1b5b1_w2280ab1b5_w2281ab1\">\n<img alt=\"Graphical content\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/labelcolorwin.jpg?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ikq1665702989159__table_d5696e1_d5697e1_d5698e1__entry__3\">\n Background is Uniface color 0\n <div class=\"p\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"ikq1665702989159__fig_w2282ab1b5b1b1b3b9b3b5b1b1_w2283ab1b5b1b1b3b9b3b5b1_w2284ab1b5b1b1b3b9b3b5_w2285ab1b5b1b1b3b9b3_w2286ab1b5b1b1b3b9_w2287ab1b5b1b1b3_w2288ab1b5b1b1_w2289ab1b5b1_w2290ab1b5_w2291ab1\">\n<img alt=\"Graphical content\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/labelcolorps.jpg?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ikq1665702989159__table_d5696e1_d5697e1_d5698e1__entry__1\">\n Labels\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ikq1665702989159__table_d5696e1_d5697e1_d5698e1__entry__2\">\n Labels can be printed in bold, italic or with underline.\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ikq1665702989159__table_d5696e1_d5697e1_d5698e1__entry__3\">\n Labels cannot be printed in bold, italic or with underline. Text is printed in the normal font.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ikq1665702989159__table_d5696e1_d5697e1_d5698e1__entry__1\">\n Underscores indicating shortcuts\n <p class=\"p\">In a label, a character that is preceded by a % sign, is rendered onscreen as an underscore.</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ikq1665702989159__table_d5696e1_d5697e1_d5698e1__entry__2\">\n Label is printed without an underscore\n <div class=\"p\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"ikq1665702989159__fig_w2292ab1b5b1b1b3b9b7b3b1b1_w2293ab1b5b1b1b3b9b7b3b1_w2294ab1b5b1b1b3b9b7b3_w2295ab1b5b1b1b3b9b7_w2296ab1b5b1b1b3b9_w2297ab1b5b1b1b3_w2298ab1b5b1b1_w2299ab1b5b1_w2300ab1b5_w2301ab1\">\n<img alt=\"Graphical content\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/labelunderscorewin.jpg?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ikq1665702989159__table_d5696e1_d5697e1_d5698e1__entry__3\">\n Label is printed with a literal % sign.\n <div class=\"p\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"ikq1665702989159__fig_w2302ab1b5b1b1b3b9b7b5b1b1_w2303ab1b5b1b1b3b9b7b5b1_w2304ab1b5b1b1b3b9b7b5_w2305ab1b5b1b1b3b9b7_w2306ab1b5b1b1b3b9_w2307ab1b5b1b1b3_w2308ab1b5b1b1_w2309ab1b5b1_w2310ab1b5_w2311ab1\">\n<img alt=\"Graphical content\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/colorprintps.jpg?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ikq1665702989159__table_d5696e1_d5697e1_d5698e1__entry__1\">\n Text wrapping in buttons\n <div class=\"p\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"ikq1665702989159__fig_w2312ab1b5b1b1b3b9b9b1b1b1_w2313ab1b5b1b1b3b9b9b1b1_w2314ab1b5b1b1b3b9b9b1_w2315ab1b5b1b1b3b9b9_w2316ab1b5b1b1b3b9_w2317ab1b5b1b1b3_w2318ab1b5b1b1_w2319ab1b5b1_w2320ab1b5_w2321ab1\">\n<img alt=\"Graphical content\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/buttontextwrapping.jpg?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ikq1665702989159__table_d5696e1_d5697e1_d5698e1__entry__2\">\n Text that does not fit the button is wrapped.\n <div class=\"p\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"ikq1665702989159__fig_w2322ab1b5b1b1b3b9b9b3b1b1_w2323ab1b5b1b1b3b9b9b3b1_w2324ab1b5b1b1b3b9b9b3_w2325ab1b5b1b1b3b9b9_w2326ab1b5b1b1b3b9_w2327ab1b5b1b1b3_w2328ab1b5b1b1_w2329ab1b5b1_w2330ab1b5_w2331ab1\">\n<img alt=\"Graphical content\" aria-label=\"Open image in gallery mode\" class=\"image expandable\" data-fancy=\"gallery\" data-gallery=\"gallery\" data-remote=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/buttontextwrappingwin.jpg?_LANG=enus\" data-title=\"\" role=\"button\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/buttontextwrappingwin.jpg?_LANG=enus\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" tabindex=\"0\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ikq1665702989159__table_d5696e1_d5697e1_d5698e1__entry__3\">\n Text that does not fit the button is clipped.\n <div class=\"p\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"ikq1665702989159__fig_w2332ab1b5b1b1b3b9b9b5b1b1_w2333ab1b5b1b1b3b9b9b5b1_w2334ab1b5b1b1b3b9b9b5_w2335ab1b5b1b1b3b9b9_w2336ab1b5b1b1b3b9_w2337ab1b5b1b1b3_w2338ab1b5b1b1_w2339ab1b5b1_w2340ab1b5_w2341ab1\">\n<img alt=\"Graphical content\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/buttontextwrappingps.jpg?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ikq1665702989159__table_d5696e1_d5697e1_d5698e1__entry__1\">\n Image aspect ratio\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ikq1665702989159__table_d5696e1_d5697e1_d5698e1__entry__2\">\n The image is clipped to the field borders, ignoring the Preserve Aspect property.\n <div class=\"p\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"ikq1665702989159__fig_w2342ab1b5b1b1b3b9c11b3b1b1_w2343ab1b5b1b1b3b9c11b3b1_w2344ab1b5b1b1b3b9c11b3_w2345ab1b5b1b1b3b9c11_w2346ab1b5b1b1b3b9_w2347ab1b5b1b1b3_w2348ab1b5b1b1_w2349ab1b5b1_w2350ab1b5_w2351ab1\">\n<img alt=\"Graphical content\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/imageaspectwin.jpg?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ikq1665702989159__table_d5696e1_d5697e1_d5698e1__entry__3\">\n The image fits the field width, and the image aspect ratio is maintained.\n <div class=\"p\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"ikq1665702989159__fig_w2352ab1b5b1b1b3b9c11b5b1b1_w2353ab1b5b1b1b3b9c11b5b1_w2354ab1b5b1b1b3b9c11b5_w2355ab1b5b1b1b3b9c11_w2356ab1b5b1b1b3b9_w2357ab1b5b1b1b3_w2358ab1b5b1b1_w2359ab1b5b1_w2360ab1b5_w2361ab1\">\n<img alt=\"Graphical content\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/imageaspectps.jpg?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ikq1665702989159__table_d5696e1_d5697e1_d5698e1__entry__1\">\n Images scaling in percentage\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ikq1665702989159__table_d5696e1_d5697e1_d5698e1__entry__2\">\n Not supported\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ikq1665702989159__table_d5696e1_d5697e1_d5698e1__entry__3\">\n Not supported\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ikq1665702989159__table_d5696e1_d5697e1_d5698e1__entry__1\">\n Transparent images\n <div class=\"p\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"ikq1665702989159__fig_w2362ab1b5b1b1b3b9c15b1b1b1_w2363ab1b5b1b1b3b9c15b1b1_w2364ab1b5b1b1b3b9c15b1_w2365ab1b5b1b1b3b9c15_w2366ab1b5b1b1b3b9_w2367ab1b5b1b1b3_w2368ab1b5b1b1_w2369ab1b5b1_w2370ab1b5_w2371ab1\">\n<img alt=\"Graphical content\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/imagetransparent.jpg?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ikq1665702989159__table_d5696e1_d5697e1_d5698e1__entry__2\">\n Background is black\n <div class=\"p\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"ikq1665702989159__fig_w2372ab1b5b1b1b3b9c15b3b1b1_w2373ab1b5b1b1b3b9c15b3b1_w2374ab1b5b1b1b3b9c15b3_w2375ab1b5b1b1b3b9c15_w2376ab1b5b1b1b3b9_w2377ab1b5b1b1b3_w2378ab1b5b1b1_w2379ab1b5b1_w2380ab1b5_w2381ab1\">\n<img alt=\"Graphical content\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/imagetransparentwin.jpg?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ikq1665702989159__table_d5696e1_d5697e1_d5698e1__entry__3\">\n Background is transparent\n <div class=\"p\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"ikq1665702989159__fig_w2382ab1b5b1b1b3b9c15b5b1b1_w2383ab1b5b1b1b3b9c15b5b1_w2384ab1b5b1b1b3b9c15b5_w2385ab1b5b1b1b3b9c15_w2386ab1b5b1b1b3b9_w2387ab1b5b1b1b3_w2388ab1b5b1b1_w2389ab1b5b1_w2390ab1b5_w2391ab1\">\n<img alt=\"Graphical content\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/imagetransparentps.jpg?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xiz1665702989085.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Device Translation Tables for Printing</a><p>Printer device tables are a collection of sequences (control codes) associated with specific logical functions (such as bold, form feed, and init). The sequences begin with the escape character and are referred to as escape sequences.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nyc1665702629732.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Color Handling</a><p>The objects that make up an application's user interface have color properties that determine foreground and background colors. These properties can be set in the Uniface IDE when defining each object, but they can also be set dynamically using ProcScript. Depending on the property, you can specify an object's color as a system color name, web color name, or RGB value (expressed as decimal or hexadecimal values).</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qsj1704711355836.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Image Handling</a><p>Uniface can display and print pictures that are stored as image files on disk, as glyphs, or BLOBs in a database. The type of picture can affect performance.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528591\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528591\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Differences Between P_MSWINX and P_X11 Output Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 07, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Differences Between P_MSWINX and P_X11 Output For enhanced printing, Uniface provides the P_MSWINX device translation table for Windows and the P_X11 table for PostScript. However, there are differences in print output produced, especially in the way colors and images are handled. Table 1. Functionality P_MSWINX P_X11 Color printing Note: Color printing is only possible if Print using colors is selected in the Print Job Model. Only index colors can be printed. Index colors can be printed. Web colors (which are set using the Background and Foreground widget properties) can be printed. Note: It is not possible to combine index colors and web colors in a single component. Color code 0 in labels Transparent background Background is Uniface color 0 Labels Labels can be printed in bold, italic or with underline. Labels cannot be printed in bold, italic or with underline. Text is printed in the normal font. Underscores indicating shortcuts In a label, a character that is preceded by a % sign, is rendered onscreen as an underscore. Label is printed without an underscore Label is printed with a literal % sign. Text wrapping in buttons Text that does not fit the button is wrapped. Text that does not fit the button is clipped. Image aspect ratio The image is clipped to the field borders, ignoring the Preserve Aspect property. The image fits the field width, and the image aspect ratio is maintained. Images scaling in percentage Not supported Not supported Transparent images Background is black Background is transparent Related Links Device Translation Tables for Printing Printer device tables are a collection of sequences (control codes) associated with specific logical functions (such as bold, form feed, and init). The sequences begin with the escape character and are referred to as escape sequences. Color Handling The objects that make up an application's user interface have color properties that determine foreground and background colors. These properties can be set in the Uniface IDE when defining each object, but they can also be set dynamically using ProcScript. Depending on the property, you can specify an object's color as a system color name, web color name, or RGB value (expressed as decimal or hexadecimal values). Image Handling Uniface can display and print pictures that are stored as image files on disk, as glyphs, or BLOBs in a database. The type of picture can affect performance. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}